```json
{
  "type": "telemetry",
  "robot_id": "tb3_01",
  "map_id": "map_01",
  "session_id": "session_tb3_01_20260307",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-07T16:20:00Z",
  "x": 1.24,
  "y": 2.81,
  "yaw": 0.52,
  "linear_x": 0.12,
  "angular_z": 0.03,
  "battery": 98.5
}
```

### Command Message
```json
{
  "type": "command",
  "robot_id": "tb3_01",
  "linear_x_cmd": 0.2,
  "angular_z_cmd": 0.0
}
```

### Goal Message
```json
{
  "type": "goal",
  "robot_id": "tb3_01",
  "x": 4.2,
  "y": 1.8,
  "yaw": 0.0
}
```

